 | publisher = John Wiley and Sons
 | year = 1999
 | isbn = 0-7803-1193-0
 | pages = 49–51
}}</ref>。他称这是“[[生物电磁学|动物電]]”。在西元1800年，[[亞歷山德羅·伏打|伏打（Volta）]]宣布发明[[伏打電堆|伏打電堆]]。

这些成果为[[電池|電池]]和电学的发展铺平了道路。伏打電池被命名为1799年的[[IEEE里程碑列表|IEEE里程碑]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ieeeghn.org/wiki/index.php/Milestones:Volta%27s_Electrical_Battery_Invention,_1799 |title=Milestones:Volta's Electrical Battery Invention, 1799 |author= |date= |work=IEEE Global History Network |publisher=IEEE |accessdate=26 July 2011 |archive-date=2015-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221083922/http://www.ieeeghn.org/wiki/index.php/Milestones:Volta's_Electrical_Battery_Invention,_1799 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

